Today it accepts all flavors of RSS		(0.90, 0.91, 0.92, 0.93, 0.94, 1.0 and 2.0), Atom 0.3 and Atom 1.0 feeds. Rome includesa set of parsers and generators for the various flavors of feeds, aswell as converters		to convert from one format to another.
